8 An Act relating to schools; amending 70 O.S. 2021,
Section 6-101.6b, which relates to whistleblower
9 protections; defining term; extending applicability
of protections to support employees; updating
10 statutory citation; providing an effective date; and
declaring an emergency.
11
12
13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 6-101.6b, is
15 amended to read as follows:
16 Section 6-101.6b. A. For purposes of this section, "teacher":
17 1. "Teacher" means the term as defined in paragraph 1 of
18 Section 1-116 of Title 70 of the Oklahoma Statutes this title; and
19 2. "Support employee" means the term as defined in paragraph 9
20 of Section 1-116 of this title.
21 B. No school district shall prohibit or take disciplinary
22 action against teachers or support employees for:
23
